      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the high-strung S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity under load. The drivetrain consists of a tactile 6-speed manual transmission feeding a factory GKN variable M-differential. Handling is sharpened via refreshed control arm bushings and monotube dampers, providing excellent feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. While the exterior reflects its status as an enjoyed driver's car, the mechanical synchronization and powertrain response remain sharp and predictable.",
